window.bookSummaryJSON = "From the <i>Chrestomanci</i> series comes book number three, <i>The Magicians of Caprona</i>. For years, the Montana family has feuded with the Petrocchi family. But Tonino Montana must seek help from the Petrocchis, and a special cat, to save the city of Caprona and prove he deserves to live among the spell-makers."; 
